Aurora.566th Intelligence Squadron:
The 566th Intelligence Squadron is a support unit to the Aerospace Data Facility in conjunction with the 460th Space Wing, Buckley Air Force Base, Colorado. The 566th is part of the 544th Intelligence, Surveillance and Reconnaissance Group, headquartered at Peterson Air Force Base, Colorado.


== Mission ==
To provide the Aerospace Data Facility-Colorado with information and technical support in the performance of joint national system missions.
